1856
01:49:51,585 --> 01:49:52,626
Be kind.

1857
01:49:56,172 --> 01:49:58,215
Hang on.

1858
01:49:58,341 --> 01:49:59,425
I think I know her.

1859
01:50:03,597 --> 01:50:04,805
Excuse me.

1860
01:50:04,931 --> 01:50:07,224
Aren't you Caroline Gund?

1861
01:50:07,350 --> 01:50:08,726
I'm Deirdre.
We met in-

