1866
01:50:16,276 --> 01:50:17,318
Hello, nice to meet.

1867
01:50:17,444 --> 01:50:18,819
Do you live here in Madrid?

1868
01:50:18,945 --> 01:50:20,863
No, no, we're just visiting.

1869
01:50:20,989 --> 01:50:22,072
We live in New York.

1870
01:50:22,198 --> 01:50:23,240
Really?
