1903
01:51:55,500 --> 01:52:00,504
Did you know
that a bee sting can be fatal?

1904
01:52:00,630 --> 01:52:03,549
Was it fatal?
Did he die?

1905
01:52:03,675 --> 01:52:05,634
No.
He recovered.

1906
01:52:05,760 --> 01:52:08,137
But it a profound
psychological effect.

1907
01:52:44,299 --> 01:52:46,175
Will you call her?

